sequenceDiagram
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant VB as Vision Box (RPi 4)
    participant Admin as Beheerder

    Note over API,VB: Systeem bevindt zich in PENDING_INSPECTION (oranje LED brandt)

    Admin->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/loans?status=PENDING_INSPECTION [JWT admin]
    API-->>Admin: Lijst van loans in quarantaine

    Admin->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/evaluations/{evaluation_id}
    API-->>Admin: Foto, AI rapport, damage details

    alt Beheerder keurt schade goed (Echte schade of Fraude)
        Admin->>API: PATCH /api/v1/admin/evaluations/{evaluation_id} {is_approved: true}
        API->>DB: UPDATE loans SET loan_status = 'DISPUTED' WHERE loan_id = {loan_id}
        API->>DB: UPDATE assets SET asset_status = 'MAINTENANCE' WHERE asset_id = {asset_id}
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs {action_type: 'DAMAGE_CONFIRMED'}
        API-->>Admin: 200 OK (Schade bevestigd, gebruiker gemarkeerd)
    else Beheerder verwerpt AI rapport (Fout-positief)
        Admin->>API: PATCH /api/v1/admin/evaluations/{evaluation_id} {is_approved: false}
        API->>DB: UPDATE loans SET loan_status = 'COMPLETED' WHERE loan_id = {loan_id}
        API->>DB: UPDATE assets SET asset_status = 'AVAILABLE', locker_id = <return_locker_id> WHERE asset_id = {asset_id}
        API->>DB: UPDATE lockers SET locker_status = 'OCCUPIED' WHERE locker_id = <return_locker_id>
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs {action_type: 'DAMAGE_REJECTED_FALSE_POSITIVE'}
        API->>VB: WSS: set_led {locker_id: <return_locker_id>, color: green}
        API-->>Admin: 200 OK (Quarantaine opgeheven)
    end